    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Once you've converted your String to a number, you can use</p>\n\n<pre><code>// format the number for the default locale\nNumberFormat.getInstance().format(num)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>// format the number for a particular locale\nNumberFormat.getInstance(locale).format(num)\n</code></pre>\n"
