    "question_id" : 3672731,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The first answer works very well, but for ZERO / 0 it will format as .00</p>\n\n<p>Hence the format #,##0.00 is working well for me.\nAlways test different numbers such as 0 / 100 / 2334.30 and negative numbers before deploying to production system.</p>\n"
