    "body" : "<pre><code>public void convert(int s)\n{\n    System.out.println(NumberFormat.getNumberInstance(Locale.US).format(s));\n}\n\npublic static void main(String args[])\n{\n    LocalEx n=new LocalEx();\n    n.convert(10000);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
