    "creation_date" : 1494140018,
    "answer_id" : 43828646,
    "question_id" : 3672731,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here is the simplest way to get there:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String number = \"10987655.876\";\ndouble result = Double.parseDouble(number);\nSystem.out.println(String.format(\"%,.2f\",result)); \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>output:\n10,987,655.88</p>\n"
